A. Gray as well as a specimen of 
<taxonomicName authority="H.Mann, 1866" authorityName="H.Mann" authorityYear="1866" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Rutaceae" genus="Platydesma" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Platydesma" order="Sapindales" pageId="6" pageNumber="131" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
